     Tesselate the given surface patch.  eval is a  routine  that
     takes  a  pointer  to  a  triangular  patch  and an array of
     Scalars, and returns a Point.  patch should be a pointer  to
     the  patch  structure  that  eval  expects.   samples is the
     number of desired samples along an edge.  frame is a coordi-
     nate frame used to extract the output coordinates.

     The surface normal and Gaussian curvature is  estimated  for
     each point.






